WEBVTT

00:00:01.101 --> 00:00:02.627
What you have here

00:00:02.651 --> 00:00:05.920
is an electronic cigarette.

00:00:06.837 --> 00:00:10.056
It's something that, since it was
invented a year or two ago,

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:11.551
has given me untold happiness.

00:00:11.575 --> 00:00:12.756
(Laughter)

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:15.215
A little bit of it,
I think, is the nicotine,

00:00:15.239 --> 00:00:17.449
but there's something
much bigger than that;

00:00:17.473 --> 00:00:23.040
which is, ever since, in the UK,
they banned smoking in public places,

00:00:23.064 --> 00:00:25.884
I've never enjoyed
a drinks party ever again.

00:00:25.908 --> 00:00:27.766
(Laughter)

00:00:27.790 --> 00:00:30.886
And the reason, I only worked out
just the other day,